The 15mm Cuban link is the most substantial piece in the catalog — nearly triple the width of the entry 6mm, with a price reflecting the significant additional gold content. This is a collector-tier piece for buyers who specifically want maximum visual impact.

**Platinum Cuban:** **[8" Men's Cuban Link Bracelet in Platinum (3.5mm)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/8-mens-cuban-link-bracelet-in-platinum-35-mm-item-150911?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)** — **$3,485**

![8" Men's Cuban Link Bracelet in Platinum (3.5 mm)](/images/822-Mens-Cuban-Link-Bracelet-in-Platinum-3.5-mm.png)

Platinum's naturally white color and greater density (approximately 60% heavier than gold by volume) makes this bracelet feel substantially more substantial on the wrist despite its 3.5mm slimness. For men who prefer white metal without the rhodium-plating maintenance of white gold, platinum is the superior choice.

**Entry via James Allen merger — Sterling Silver:** **[Miami Cuban Bracelet In Sterling Silver (8.5") By James Allen](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/miami-cuban-bracelet-in-sterling-silver-85-by-james-allen-item-315974?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)** — **$570**

The James Allen sterling silver Cuban is the most accessible entry point in the entire catalog — and the only sterling silver option.

For buyers who want the Cuban link look without the gold investment, this provides the aesthetic at a fraction of the price. Sterling silver tarnishes more readily than gold and requires occasional polishing, but the $570 price point is genuinely attractive.

### **Cuban Link: Who Should Buy Which Width?**

-   **Wrist under 7":** 6mm or 7.3mm — wider widths can overwhelm a small wrist
-   **Wrist 7"–7.5":** 7.3mm–9.3mm is the sweet spot
-   **Wrist over 8":** 11mm or 15mm reads proportionally
-   **Daily office wear:** 6mm or 7.3mm — subtle enough for professional environments
-   **Weekend/casual:** 9.3mm or 11mm — reads as intentional jewelry
-   **Maximum statement:** 15mm — for buyers who specifically want the bold Cuban aesthetic

## **Chain Bracelets: Seven Styles Compared**

**Blue Nile's chain bracelet selection covers seven distinct link patterns — each with different optical character, weight, and daily-wear suitability.**

### **1\. Figaro Chain Bracelet**

The Figaro pattern alternates one long oval link with two to three shorter round links in a repeating sequence. It is one of the most recognized chain patterns globally — originating in Italy and associated with classic masculine jewelry.

**Entry level (James Allen merger):** **[Figaro Chain Bracelet In 14K Yellow Gold (8") By James Allen](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/figaro-chain-bracelet-in-14k-yellow-gold-8-by-james-allen-item-315756?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)** — **$990** (available in multiple lengths)

![Figaro Chain Bracelet In 14K Yellow Gold (8") By James Allen](/images/Figaro-Chain-Bracelet-In-14K-Yellow-Gold-822-By-James-Allen.png)

**Standard Figaro — 4mm flat:** **[8" Flat Figaro Chain Bracelet in 14K White Gold (4mm)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/8-flat-figaro-chain-bracelet-in-14k-white-gold-4-mm-item-147965?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)** — **$970** (1 review)

**Heavy Figaro — 7.5mm:** **[8" Men's Figaro Chain Bracelet in 14K Yellow Gold (7.5mm)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/8-mens-figaro-chain-bracelet-in-14k-yellow-gold-75-mm-item-193894?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)** — **$4,500** (4 reviews)

The jump from $970 (4mm) to $4,500 (7.5mm) reflects nearly double the metal width — and nearly quadruple the price. The 7.5mm Figaro has 4 reviews, making it the most-reviewed chain bracelet in the catalog after the 6mm Cuban.

**Maximum Figaro — 8.75mm flat:** **[8" Flat Figaro Chain Bracelet in 14K Yellow Gold (8.75mm)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/8-flat-figaro-chain-bracelet-in-14k-yellow-gold-875-mm-item-147967?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)** — **$4,500**

**Platinum Figaro:** **[8" Men's Flat Figaro Chain Bracelet in Platinum (3.2mm)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/8-mens-flat-figaro-chain-bracelet-bracelet-in-platinum-32-mm-item-150905?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)** — **$2,805**

