At 3.2mm in platinum, this is the most refined Figaro option — slim, dense, and distinctly premium. The natural white of platinum requires no rhodium plating unlike white gold.

### **2\. Rope Chain Bracelet**

The rope chain features spiral-twisted links that create a helical pattern mimicking twisted rope. It is inherently reflective — the multiple surfaces catch light from many angles simultaneously.

**Standard rope — 6mm:** **[8" Rope Chain Bracelet in 14K Yellow Gold (6mm)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/8-rope-chain-bracelet-in-14k-yellow-gold-6-mm-item-147972?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)** — **$4,365**

**Diamond-cut rope — 5.5mm:** **[8" Diamond Cut Rope Chain Bracelet in 14K Yellow Gold (5.5mm)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/8-diamond-cut-rope-chain-bracelet-in-14k-yellow-gold-55-mm-item-147971?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)** — **$4,345**

![8" Diamond Cut Rope Chain Bracelet in 14k Yellow Gold (5.5 mm)](/images/822-Diamond-Cut-Rope-Chain-Bracelet-in-14k-Yellow-Gold-5.5-mm.png)

The "diamond cut" designation does not involve diamonds — it refers to facets machine-cut into the metal links to maximize light reflection. A diamond-cut rope catches more light than a standard rope of the same width, producing a brighter, more active sparkle.

**James Allen solid rope (multiple lengths):** **[Solid Rope Chain Bracelet In 14K Yellow Gold (8") By James Allen](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/solid-rope-chain-bracelet-in-14k-yellow-gold-8-by-james-allen-item-316270?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)** — **$1,675**

**[Solid Rope Chain Bracelet In 14K Yellow Gold (8") By James Allen](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/solid-rope-chain-bracelet-in-14k-yellow-gold-8-by-james-allen-item-316271?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)** — **$1,740**

The two James Allen solid rope options at $1,675 and $1,740 represent different weight specifications for the same listed length — the $65 difference reflects different metal content. Verify the gram weight listed on each product page before purchasing.

